Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Rurino-chan!!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.47,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What was that farewell letter supposed to mean!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:07.96,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Guh–!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She… she’s running away!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:16.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Why!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:23.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Can you not follow me!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:28.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hey, why’d you ditch practice!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Do you hate singing that much!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:37.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she’s not feeling well!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:41.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But isn’t she running too fast for that!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.72,Kaho,,0,0,0,, There’s no way she’s sick! No way!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Then why is she running away!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:52.54,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And why are we chasing her!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:56.34,Kaho,,0,0,0,,If she’s running away, isn’t it only natural to chase after her!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:57.90,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don’t get it!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:03.65,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Agh, give it up already!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:06.04,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Wait, is she getting on that bus!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.28,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san, if we keep going, then–\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.04,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But why!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Agh… haaah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:24.13,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I-I can’t believe… you chased me all the way here…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:27.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Why?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don’t get it at all, either…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:36.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,B-Because… you just went… and ran away from us…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:42.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What’s… wrong?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.57,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Is… something wrong…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m just guessing, but…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:55.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’d bet that Kaho-san would have chased you to the ends of the earth until you sat down and talked to her…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:57.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She’s very passionate…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:04.37,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:05.48,NPC,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HC38353&\4c&HAF6E3D&}H{*\3c&H9C896F&\4c&H96704F&}u{*\3c&H75908B&\4c&H7D7360&}h{*\3c&H4E96A7&\4c&H647572&}!{*\3c&H279DC3&\4c&H4B7883&}?{\3c&H00A3DF&\4c&H327A95&}\N{\fs40}{\3c&HC38353&\4c&HAF6E3D&}[{*\3c&HB6855C&\4c&HA76F43&}S{*\3c&HA98766&\4c&H9E7049&}a{*\3c&H9C896F&\4c&H96704F&}y{*\3c&H8F8C78&\4c&H8E7154&}a{*\3c&H828E82&\4c&H85725A&}k{*\3c&H75908B&\4c&H7D7360&}a {*\3c&H5B949E&\4c&H6C746C&}& {*\3c&H4198B0&\4c&H5C7678&}K{*\3c&H349ABA&\4c&H53777E&}a{*\3c&H279DC3&\4c&H4B7883&}h{*\3c&H1A9FCC&\4c&H437889&}o{*\3c&H0DA1D6&\4c&H3A798F&}]{\3c&H00A3DF&\4c&H327A95&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:35.88,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahh…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.18,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Now this is summer…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.21,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-whoa!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,All the soda’s spilling out!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this really the time for ramune!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:57.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Umm, I am… terribly sorry for causing this incident…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:03.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I truly had intended on immediately returning to practice. However…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:10.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I instead have caused considerable inconvenience for all parties, including Mistress Kozue and Mistress Tsuzuri.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I must offer my humblest apologies…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.64,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’ve never heard such a corporate apology before…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I am just a water flea, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.67,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Wait, why are we at the batting cages?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.41,Kaho,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, well!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:31.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s my first time coming to one of these places! It’s actually kinda fun, huh!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hahaha, it sure is!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Haaah.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.34,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I can’t do this…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,My battery’s fully drained.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.16,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.18,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What started all this…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.58,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it so bad you can’t talk about it!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it’s not…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:03.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m just… not in social mode right now.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.95,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,By any chance, Rurino-san…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:11.23,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Have you been forcing yourself this whole time?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Not really, but…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Well… ah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure… that.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She clearly gave up on explaining!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I don’t mind talking about it, but…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:37.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s just nothin’ special, y’know?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.92,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Would you… talk to us about it?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:45.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’ll keep a tab on Kaho-san.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.91,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…I really like it when things are lively,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:57.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,but when they’re always like that, I tend to get drained really easily…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.86,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And that’s not because…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,you were forcing yourself… to be with us…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Nah.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m totally serious when I say the School Idol Club is really fun,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,and you’re all such nice people.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.20,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s just…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:20.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,When people start caring about me, I try to give them as much care in return,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.19,Rurino,,0,0,0,,and that starts draining my battery even faster.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And now I’m just in airplane mode.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.60,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So you worry too much about other people?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,If it’s like that, you don’t have to worry about us!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.75,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Nah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:42.69,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s hard for me not to…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.36,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:49.16,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think I somewhat understand where you’re coming from.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.59,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But… that’s why…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You don’t have to work yourself this hard…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Look, I really get that.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I just… can’t.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:03.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,No matter what I’ve tried, nothing changes.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:08.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And since we all take the time to get together, it’s not just about me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to have fun, too.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:21.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t help anyone if I’m like this, y’know.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.06,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So this is your…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:27.26,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,“dead battery mode,” is it, Rurino-san?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:32.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This seems very serious…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:37.13,Rurino,,0,0,0,,When I’m like this, I can’t really do much…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.53,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Just gotta sit tight and wait to recharge…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:48.18,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And I would hate to make other people worry about me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:53.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,‘Cause then you’d all have to cover for me, and then you’d start having less fun…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:58.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So, I figured it’d be best for me to stick to myself…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah, but listen!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I don’t want you to get it twisted!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m totally fine being alone.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Things like having a solo batting cage outing can feel like a royal feast to me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:18.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku also became much easier solo, so in fact, I {\i1}welcome{\i0} it.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:23.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So, I’m totally, completely, one hundred percent fine with being alone!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.77,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m not pretending or anything.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:29.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I can find my own fun, all by myself.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.11,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Seriously!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.57,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Sorry ‘bout making this whole thing all weird, okay!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:40.14,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Everything’s so awkward now ‘cuz of me…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So, um.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Take this.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.27,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.73,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Is that…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.19,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,a club resignation application…!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huuuuh!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
